            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and the mountains will be like carded wool"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "So as for those whose scale is heavy ˹with good deeds˺"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "they will be in a life of bliss"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "And as for those whose scale is light"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "their home will be the abyss"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And what will make you realize what that is"
